Domain classes used to produce all classes which directly interact with the Ivy bus.

    Class Description
    AckCallback

    AudioCallback

    DieCallback
    DieCallback is the class removing the flight from the array parametresVol

    FlightCallback is the class used to store parameters of flights reveive in the Ivy bus.
    IvyManager
    IvyManager is the class which manage the information send through and with Ivy
    OrderCallback
